WEBVTT

00:00:02.450 --> 00:00:10.050
When we heard that there would be a special convention in Madagascar, we were very happy.

00:00:10.050 --> 00:00:13.609
We said we have to get there.

00:00:13.609 --> 00:00:17.850
We decided to increase the amount of soap we make so that we could pay for the travel

00:00:17.850 --> 00:00:19.010
to the convention.

00:00:19.010 --> 00:00:25.250
We have three children who are going to be baptized in Antananarivo.

00:00:25.250 --> 00:00:30.329
As a family, we have worked together to make breaks so that we can pay the fare for

00:00:30.329 --> 00:00:33.369
this special event in our life.

00:00:33.369 --> 00:00:40.200
We are looking forward to meet brothers and sisters from around the world.

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:47.100
I make earrings and I sell them.

00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:51.920
I will use the money to attend the convention.

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:55.600
I am very happy.

00:00:55.600 --> 00:01:01.000
I make bags with these Vulpika beans to get some money to attend the convention.

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:02.000
This is my pig.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:05.560
I will sell it so that I can attend the convention.

00:01:05.599 --> 00:01:07.519
I am raising chickens.

00:01:07.519 --> 00:01:12.000
I am doing laundry.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:18.760
Visiting delegates for traveling form from nine countries to come to Madagascar.

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:23.000
We're taking with us some necklaces and bracelets from South Africa to give to the

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:38.170
brothers and sisters in Madagascar.

00:01:38.170 --> 00:01:42.489
From the very moment we showed up, you could just feel that love from all of the friends

00:01:42.489 --> 00:01:45.650
and welcome, welcome, welcome is the message we kept getting.

00:01:45.689 --> 00:01:47.409
We really enjoyed the tour of the branch.

00:01:47.409 --> 00:01:51.530
They also had dancing and wonderful food.

00:01:51.530 --> 00:01:55.730
One theme that I saw with all of the local friends here is they were all smiling from

00:01:55.730 --> 00:01:56.730
ear to ear.

00:01:56.730 --> 00:02:01.329
A lot of energy too, great, happy energy.

00:02:01.329 --> 00:02:04.930
The ministry was incredible and we had the friends there right by our side to help us

00:02:04.930 --> 00:02:07.299
along.

00:02:07.299 --> 00:02:12.460
You've seen Jehovah's creation in an area where it's been untouched and you get to see

00:02:12.460 --> 00:02:16.500
some of the plants and animals you can't see anywhere else in the world is truly a

00:02:16.500 --> 00:02:17.500
nice blessing.

00:02:17.500 --> 00:02:26.139
Even on our large island, many people have far to travel, some walk on foot for several

00:02:26.139 --> 00:02:27.139
days.

00:02:27.139 --> 00:02:33.020
Many take a pass journey of a few days to arrive here in the tent and the river.

00:02:33.020 --> 00:04:02.539
But everyone is eager to be at the special convention in Madagascar.

00:04:02.539 --> 00:04:09.139
Now when I think about my three children who got baptized today, I feel my heart is full

00:04:09.139 --> 00:04:14.530
of joy and I really thank Jehovah.

00:04:14.530 --> 00:04:19.610
We walked for three days with our congregation and then we took a pass.

00:04:19.610 --> 00:04:24.889
We arrived safely in Atalanarivo because we did not cave up.

00:04:24.889 --> 00:04:27.730
We are so happy to be here.

00:04:27.730 --> 00:04:33.209
Even though I do not know all these people from before, they are Jehovah's people and

00:04:33.250 --> 00:04:35.170
I can get to love them.

00:04:35.170 --> 00:04:38.610
I've never been in a stadium with so many people.

00:04:38.610 --> 00:04:44.610
Just to see that many people singing to Jehovah was quite an experience and it made me

00:04:44.610 --> 00:04:49.730
think, wow, this is like a taste of paradise.

00:04:49.730 --> 00:04:54.769
I am in the organization for 47 years now.

00:04:54.769 --> 00:05:00.129
This is something that really makes me happy and it encourages me to see such a great

00:05:00.129 --> 00:05:06.139
crowd, which is benefiting greatly from Jehovah himself.

00:05:06.139 --> 00:05:12.379
This is our very first special convention and everything has exceeded all of my expectations.

00:05:12.379 --> 00:05:15.899
It makes me think, wow, what is Jehovah having to do next?
